item.title: Superman: Birthright (2003 - 2004)
item.description: Superman: Birthright: The Origin of the Man of Steel. Mark Waid. Image Credits: dc.com Superman: Birthright. Mark Waid; Leinil Francis Yu; Gerry Alanguilan; Dave McCaig. www.dc.com . www.hoopladigital.com . 2003. Accessed Mar 24, 2023. Snapshots JOR-EL. For the thousand orbits, a shining planet circled a celestial font of heat and light. The people of that world grew tired of war so they achieved a united society.
